    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      With over 50 years of proven legacy, Chandak Electricals is a hallmark of trust, commitment, and engineering precision in the electrical industry. Based in Nagpur, we are a leading supplier and contractor serving across two core verticals: <strong>electrical product supply</strong> and <strong>turnkey electrical contracting</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      We have successfully delivered quality-driven services for residential, commercial, and industrial applications. Our team combines years of field experience with strong technical know-how to deliver end-to-end solutions—from product procurement and consultation to execution and after-sales support.
    </p>
    <p>
      We prioritize <strong>transparency, trust, and timely delivery</strong> in every client interaction. Our loyal customer base, built through consistent service, speaks volumes of the values we uphold—precision, professionalism, and personal connection.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether it's powering critical infrastructure or lighting up homes, Chandak Electricals continues to serve with the same spirit of excellence, reliability, and innovation that shaped our journey since day one.
